'''Bukky Abaniwonda''', uzwi cyane ku izina rya '''Bukky Wonder''', ni umukinnyi wa filime ukomoka muri [[Kanada]] na [[Nigeriya]]. <ref name="pulse">https://www.pulse.ng/entertainment/celebrities/bukky-abaniwonda-actress-speaks-about-her-sojourn-to-acting/kn17mbv</ref> Azwi cyane muri firime ''Bridges'',''Awkward Things About Losing Weight'' and ''The Carperdian''. <ref>https://damiadeniyi.com/bukky-abaniwonda-is-ready-for-nollywood/</ref>

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yavukiye muri [[Kanada]] nkuwa kabiri mu muryango . Yabayeho mu bwana bwe i [[Abuja]] . Afite barumuna be na bashiki be babiri. Yize Command Day Secondary School, Abuja kugirango yige amashuri yisumbuye. Hanyuma yarangije icyiciro cya comptabilite muri kaminuza ya Bowen . 

== Umwuga ==
Muri 2017, yakinnye cyane muri film ''Bridges'' iyobowe na Rogers Ofime . <ref>https://naijagists.com/canada-based-nigerian-actress-bukky-abaniwonda-returns-home-to-explore-nollywood/</ref> Hanyuma yakinnye muri film ''The End''. <ref>https://thenationonlineng.net/bukky-abaniwonda-gears-nollywood/</ref> <ref>https://www.vanguardngr.com/2017/02/bukky-abaniwonda-mission-fight-violence-women-movies/</ref>

Mu 2020, Abaniwonda yayoboye filimi ya  mbere  hagati ya Africa na Canada ''African Family'' yakorewe muri black production. yafatiwe amashusho i Calgary. Muri aba bakinnyi harimo abakinnyi b'Abanyafrika baturutse muri [[Nijeriya]], [[Repubulika Iharanira Demokarasi ya Kongo|Congo]] na [[Angola]] . <ref>https://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/calgary/alberta-calgary-african-tv-film-1.5783674</ref> <ref>[https://web.archive.org/web/20201113150737/https://www.sootoday.com/global-news/first-of-its-kind-african-canadian-film-production-in-calgary-showcases-black-talent-2825228 https://web.archive.org/web/20201113150737/https://www.sootoday.com/global-news/first-of-its-kind-african-canadian-film-production-in-calgary-showcases-black-talent-282522]</ref>

